-- Citic Group to List in Hong Kong in 2011, Joining Units, Newspaper Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-23T01:10:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/citic-group-to-list-in-hong-kong-in-2011-joining-units-newspaper-reports.html

          
          
             Citic Group plans to list in Hong
Kong by 2011, the China Business News reported today, citing an
unidentified person.  
 The Beijing-based company currently has listed units
including Citic Pacific Ltd., China CITIC Bank Corp. and CITIC
Securities Co.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Jian Guo Jiang in Shanghai at 
 jjiang@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        